local Players = game:GetService("Players") local TweenService = game:GetService("TweenService") local playerGui = Players.LocalPlayer:WaitForChild("PlayerGui") -- Remove existing notification if any if playerGui:FindFirstChild("FWSDNotification") then playerGui.FWSDNotification:Destroy() end local screenGui = Instance.new("ScreenGui", playerGui) screenGui.Name = "FWSDNotification" screenGui.IgnoreGuiInset = true screenGui.ResetOnSpawn = false local frame = Instance.new("Frame", screenGui) frame.Size = UDim2.new(0, 300, 0, 60) frame.Position = UDim2.new(1, -320, 1, -20) -- bottom right corner with 20px margin frame.AnchorPoint = Vector2.new(0, 1) -- anchor bottom-left of frame to position frame.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(20, 80, 200) frame.BackgroundTransparency = 1 frame.BorderSizePixel = 0 local corner = Instance.new("UICorner", frame) corner.CornerRadius = UDim.new(0, 10) local icon = Instance.new("TextLabel", frame) icon.Size = UDim2.new(0, 24, 0, 24) icon.Position = UDim2.new(0, 10, 0.5, -12) -- vertically center icon with offset icon.BackgroundTransparency = 1 icon.Text = "âœ“" -- Unicode checkmark icon.TextColor3 = Color3.new(0, 1, 0) -- bright green checkmark color icon.TextScaled = true icon.Font = Enum.Font.GothamBold icon.TextTransparency = 1 local text = Instance.new("TextLabel", frame) text.Size = UDim2.new(1, -50, 1, 0) -- fill width minus icon space text.Position = UDim2.new(0, 44, 0, 0) text.BackgroundTransparency = 1 text.Text = "[FWSD] Injected Successfully" text.TextColor3 = Color3.new(1, 1, 1) text.TextTransparency = 1 text.TextSize = 18 text.Font = Enum.Font.GothamSemibold text.TextXAlignment = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left -- Fade in the notification TweenService:Create(frame, TweenInfo.new(0.4), {BackgroundTransparency = 0.05}):Play() TweenService:Create(icon, TweenInfo.new(0.4), {TextTransparency = 0}):Play() TweenService:Create(text, TweenInfo.new(0.4), {TextTransparency = 0}):Play() -- Auto fade out after 4 seconds task.delay(4, function() TweenService:Create(frame, TweenInfo.new(0.4), {BackgroundTransparency = 1}):Play() TweenService:Create(icon, TweenInfo.new(0.4), {TextTransparency = 1}):Play() TweenService:Create(text, TweenInfo.new(0.4), {TextTransparency = 1}):Play() task.wait(0.5) screenGui:Destroy() end)
